151 TYPED_TEST_P(CollisionDetectorTest, ContactReporting)
152 {
153  collision_detection::CollisionRequest req;
154  req.contacts = true;
155  req.max_contacts = 1;
156 
157  moveit::core::RobotState robot_state(this->robot_model_);
158  robot_state.setToDefaultValues();
159  robot_state.update();
160 
161  Eigen::Isometry3d offset = Eigen::Isometry3d::Identity();
162  offset.translation().x() = .01;
163 
164  // robot_state.getLinkState("base_link")->updateGivenGlobalLinkTransform(Eigen::Isometry3d::Identity());
165  // robot_state.getLinkState("base_bellow_link")->updateGivenGlobalLinkTransform(offset);
166  // robot_state.getLinkState("r_gripper_palm_link")->updateGivenGlobalLinkTransform(Eigen::Isometry3d::Identity());
167  // robot_state.getLinkState("l_gripper_palm_link")->updateGivenGlobalLinkTransform(offset);
168 
169  robot_state.updateStateWithLinkAt("base_link", Eigen::Isometry3d::Identity());
170  robot_state.updateStateWithLinkAt("base_bellow_link", offset);
171  robot_state.updateStateWithLinkAt("r_gripper_palm_link", Eigen::Isometry3d::Identity());
172  robot_state.updateStateWithLinkAt("l_gripper_palm_link", offset);
173  robot_state.update();
174 
175  this->acm_->setEntry("base_link", "base_bellow_link", false);
176  this->acm_->setEntry("r_gripper_palm_link", "l_gripper_palm_link", false);
177 
178  collision_detection::CollisionResult res;
179  this->cenv_->checkSelfCollision(req, res, robot_state, *this->acm_);
180  ASSERT_TRUE(res.collision);
181  EXPECT_EQ(res.contacts.size(), 1u);
182  EXPECT_EQ(res.contacts.begin()->second.size(), 1u);
183 
184  res.clear();
185  req.max_contacts = 2;
186  req.max_contacts_per_pair = 1;
187  // req.verbose = true;
188  this->cenv_->checkSelfCollision(req, res, robot_state, *this->acm_);
189  ASSERT_TRUE(res.collision);
190  EXPECT_EQ(res.contacts.size(), 2u);
191  EXPECT_EQ(res.contacts.begin()->second.size(), 1u);
192 
193  res.contacts.clear();
194  res.contact_count = 0;
195 
196  req.max_contacts = 10;
197  req.max_contacts_per_pair = 2;
198  this->acm_ =
199  std::make_shared<collision_detection::AllowedCollisionMatrix>(this->robot_model_->getLinkModelNames(), false);
200  this->cenv_->checkSelfCollision(req, res, robot_state, *this->acm_);
201  ASSERT_TRUE(res.collision);
202  EXPECT_LE(res.contacts.size(), 10u);
203  EXPECT_LE(res.contact_count, 10u);
204 }

206 TYPED_TEST_P(CollisionDetectorTest, ContactPositions)
207 {
208  collision_detection::CollisionRequest req;
209  req.contacts = true;
210  req.max_contacts = 1;
211 
212  moveit::core::RobotState robot_state(this->robot_model_);
213  robot_state.setToDefaultValues();
214  robot_state.update();
215 
216  Eigen::Isometry3d pos1 = Eigen::Isometry3d::Identity();
217  Eigen::Isometry3d pos2 = Eigen::Isometry3d::Identity();
218 
219  pos1.translation().x() = 5.0;
220  pos2.translation().x() = 5.01;
221 
222  // robot_state.getLinkState("r_gripper_palm_link")->updateGivenGlobalLinkTransform(pos1);
223  // robot_state.getLinkState("l_gripper_palm_link")->updateGivenGlobalLinkTransform(pos2);
224  robot_state.updateStateWithLinkAt("r_gripper_palm_link", pos1);
225  robot_state.updateStateWithLinkAt("l_gripper_palm_link", pos2);
226  robot_state.update();
227 
228  this->acm_->setEntry("r_gripper_palm_link", "l_gripper_palm_link", false);
229 
230  collision_detection::CollisionResult res;
231  this->cenv_->checkSelfCollision(req, res, robot_state, *this->acm_);
232  ASSERT_TRUE(res.collision);
233  ASSERT_EQ(res.contacts.size(), 1u);
234  ASSERT_EQ(res.contacts.begin()->second.size(), 1u);
235 
236  for (collision_detection::CollisionResult::ContactMap::const_iterator it = res.contacts.begin();
237  it != res.contacts.end(); it++)
238  {
239  EXPECT_NEAR(it->second[0].pos.x(), 5.0, .33);
240  }
241 
242  pos1 = Eigen::Isometry3d(Eigen::Translation3d(3.0, 0.0, 0.0) * Eigen::Quaterniond::Identity());
243  pos2 = Eigen::Isometry3d(Eigen::Translation3d(3.0, 0.0, 0.0) *
244  Eigen::Quaterniond(sqrt(1 - pow(0.258, 2)), 0.0, 0.258, 0.0));
245  // robot_state.getLinkState("r_gripper_palm_link")->updateGivenGlobalLinkTransform(pos1);
246  // robot_state.getLinkState("l_gripper_palm_link")->updateGivenGlobalLinkTransform(pos2);
247  robot_state.updateStateWithLinkAt("r_gripper_palm_link", pos1);
248  robot_state.updateStateWithLinkAt("l_gripper_palm_link", pos2);
249  robot_state.update();
250 
251  collision_detection::CollisionResult res2;
252  this->cenv_->checkSelfCollision(req, res2, robot_state, *this->acm_);
253  ASSERT_TRUE(res2.collision);
254  ASSERT_EQ(res2.contacts.size(), 1u);
255  ASSERT_EQ(res2.contacts.begin()->second.size(), 1u);
256 
257  for (collision_detection::CollisionResult::ContactMap::const_iterator it = res2.contacts.begin();
258  it != res2.contacts.end(); it++)
259  {
260  EXPECT_NEAR(it->second[0].pos.x(), 3.0, 0.33);
261  }
262 
263  pos1 = Eigen::Isometry3d(Eigen::Translation3d(3.0, 0.0, 0.0) * Eigen::Quaterniond::Identity());
264  pos2 = Eigen::Isometry3d(Eigen::Translation3d(3.0, 0.0, 0.0) *
265  Eigen::Quaterniond(M_PI / 4.0, 0.0, M_PI / 4.0, 0.0).normalized());
266  // robot_state.getLinkState("r_gripper_palm_link")->updateGivenGlobalLinkTransform(pos1);
267  // robot_state.getLinkState("l_gripper_palm_link")->updateGivenGlobalLinkTransform(pos2);
268  robot_state.updateStateWithLinkAt("r_gripper_palm_link", pos1);
269  robot_state.updateStateWithLinkAt("l_gripper_palm_link", pos2);
270  robot_state.update();
271 
272  collision_detection::CollisionResult res3;
273  this->cenv_->checkSelfCollision(req, res2, robot_state, *this->acm_);
274  ASSERT_FALSE(res3.collision);
275 }

277 TYPED_TEST_P(CollisionDetectorTest, AttachedBodyTester)
278 {
279  collision_detection::CollisionRequest req;
280  collision_detection::CollisionResult res;
281 
282  this->acm_ =
283  std::make_shared<collision_detection::AllowedCollisionMatrix>(this->robot_model_->getLinkModelNames(), true);
284 
285  moveit::core::RobotState robot_state(this->robot_model_);
286  robot_state.setToDefaultValues();
287  robot_state.update();
288 
289  Eigen::Isometry3d pos1 = Eigen::Isometry3d::Identity();
290  pos1.translation().x() = 5.0;
291 
292  // robot_state.getLinkState("r_gripper_palm_link")->updateGivenGlobalLinkTransform(pos1);
293  robot_state.updateStateWithLinkAt("r_gripper_palm_link", pos1);
294  robot_state.update();
295  this->cenv_->checkSelfCollision(req, res, robot_state, *this->acm_);
296  ASSERT_FALSE(res.collision);
297 
298  shapes::Shape* shape = new shapes::Box(.1, .1, .1);
299  this->cenv_->getWorld()->addToObject("box", pos1, shapes::ShapeConstPtr(shape), Eigen::Isometry3d::Identity());
300 
301  res = collision_detection::CollisionResult();
302  this->cenv_->checkRobotCollision(req, res, robot_state, *this->acm_);
303  ASSERT_TRUE(res.collision);
304 
305  // deletes shape
306  this->cenv_->getWorld()->removeObject("box");
307 
308  shape = new shapes::Box(.1, .1, .1);
309  std::vector<shapes::ShapeConstPtr> shapes;
310  EigenSTL::vector_Isometry3d poses;
311  shapes.push_back(shapes::ShapeConstPtr(shape));
312  poses.push_back(Eigen::Isometry3d::Identity());
313  std::vector<std::string> touch_links;
314  robot_state.attachBody("box", poses[0], shapes, poses, touch_links, "r_gripper_palm_link");
315 
316  res = collision_detection::CollisionResult();
317  this->cenv_->checkSelfCollision(req, res, robot_state, *this->acm_);
318  ASSERT_TRUE(res.collision);
319 
320  // deletes shape
321  robot_state.clearAttachedBody("box");
322 
323  touch_links.push_back("r_gripper_palm_link");
324  touch_links.push_back("r_gripper_motor_accelerometer_link");
325  shapes[0] = std::make_shared<shapes::Box>(.1, .1, .1);
326  robot_state.attachBody("box", poses[0], shapes, poses, touch_links, "r_gripper_palm_link");
327  robot_state.update();
328 
329  res = collision_detection::CollisionResult();
330  this->cenv_->checkSelfCollision(req, res, robot_state, *this->acm_);
331  ASSERT_FALSE(res.collision);
332 
333  pos1.translation().x() = 5.01;
334  shapes::Shape* coll = new shapes::Box(.1, .1, .1);
335  this->cenv_->getWorld()->addToObject("coll", pos1, shapes::ShapeConstPtr(coll), Eigen::Isometry3d::Identity());
336  res = collision_detection::CollisionResult();
337  this->cenv_->checkRobotCollision(req, res, robot_state, *this->acm_);
338  ASSERT_TRUE(res.collision);
339 
340  this->acm_->setEntry("coll", "r_gripper_palm_link", true);
341  res = collision_detection::CollisionResult();
342  this->cenv_->checkRobotCollision(req, res, robot_state, *this->acm_);
343  ASSERT_TRUE(res.collision);
344 }

372  poses.push_back(Eigen::Isometry3d::Identity());
373 
374  std::vector<std::string> touch_links;
375  robot_state.attachBody("kinect", poses[0], shapes, poses, touch_links, "r_gripper_palm_link");
376 
377  before = ros::WallTime::now();
378  new_cenv->checkSelfCollision(req, res, robot_state);
379  first_check = (ros::WallTime::now() - before).toSec();
380  before = ros::WallTime::now();
381  new_cenv->checkSelfCollision(req, res, robot_state);
382  second_check = (ros::WallTime::now() - before).toSec();
383 
384  // the first check is going to take a while, as data must be constructed
385  EXPECT_LT(second_check, .1);
386 
387  collision_detection::CollisionEnvPtr other_new_cenv = this->value_->allocateEnv(this->cenv_, this->cenv_->getWorld());
388  before = ros::WallTime::now();
389  new_cenv->checkSelfCollision(req, res, robot_state);
390  first_check = (ros::WallTime::now() - before).toSec();
391  before = ros::WallTime::now();
392  new_cenv->checkSelfCollision(req, res, robot_state);
393  second_check = (ros::WallTime::now() - before).toSec();
394 
395  EXPECT_LT(fabs(first_check - second_check), .05);
396 }

398 TYPED_TEST_P(CollisionDetectorTest, ConvertObjectToAttached)

405  Eigen::Isometry3d pos2 = Eigen::Isometry3d::Identity();

413 
414  ros::WallTime before = ros::WallTime::now();

418  this->cenv_->checkRobotCollision(req, res, robot_state);

443  "r_gripper_palm_link");
444 
445  // going to take a while, but that's fine

448 
449  EXPECT_TRUE(res.collision);
450 
451  before = ros::WallTime::now();
452  this->cenv_->checkSelfCollision(req, res, robot_state1, *this->acm_);
453  first_check = (ros::WallTime::now() - before).toSec();
454  before = ros::WallTime::now();
455  req.verbose = true;
456  res = collision_detection::CollisionResult();
457  this->cenv_->checkSelfCollision(req, res, robot_state2, *this->acm_);
458  second_check = (ros::WallTime::now() - before).toSec();
459 
460  EXPECT_LT(first_check, .05);
461  EXPECT_LT(fabs(first_check - second_check), .1);

507 TYPED_TEST_P(CollisionDetectorTest, TestChangingShapeSize)
508 {
509  moveit::core::RobotState robot_state1(this->robot_model_);
510  robot_state1.setToDefaultValues();
511  robot_state1.update();
512 
513  collision_detection::CollisionRequest req1;
514  collision_detection::CollisionResult res1;
515 
516  ASSERT_FALSE(res1.collision);
517 
518  EigenSTL::vector_Isometry3d poses;
